Name: OCT data & Color Fundus Images of Left & Right Eyes
Abstract: This dataset contains OCT data (in mat format) and color fundus data (in jpg format) of left & right eyes of 50 healthy persons.
RelevantInfo: OCT data & Color Fundus Images of Left & Right Eyes : This dataset contains OCT data (in mat format) and color fundus data (in jpg format) of left & right eyes of 50 healthy persons. Each volunteer's folder includes color fundus images (.jpg) and OCT data (.mat) of the right and left eyes.
Source: Tahereh Mahmudi; Rahele Kafieh; Hossein Rabbani; Alireza Mehri dehnavi; Mohammadreza Akhlagi
